# Existing Hooks

Check these hooks before writing new client logic. All are in `@/hooks/`.

## Feature CRUD Hooks
| Hook | Manages | Returns |
|------|---------|---------|
| `useGuestbook` | Guestbook entries | `entries, createEntry, updateEntry, deleteEntry, isOwned, canDelete, canEdit, getTokenForEntry` |
| `usePuzzles` | Puzzle entries | `entries, createEntry, updateEntry, deleteEntry, isOwned, canDelete` |
| `useBlog` | Blog posts | `posts, createPost, updatePost, deletePost, refreshPosts` |
| `useTodos` | Todo items | `todos, addTodo, updateTodo, deleteTodo, toggleComplete, updateStatus, assignTodo, pendingTodos, completedTodos, getTodosByStatus` |
| `useLoonDelete` | Loon delete flow | `deleteTarget, isDeleting, requestDelete, confirmDelete, cancelDelete` |

## Expense Hooks
| Hook | Manages | Returns |
|------|---------|---------|
| `useExpenseVoting` | Vote score/state | `localVoteScore, localUserVote, isVoting, handleVote` |
| `useExpenseComments` | Comment CRUD | `localComments, commentText, setCommentText, handleAddComment, handleDeleteComment` |

## Utility Hooks
| Hook | Purpose | Returns |
|------|---------|---------|
| `useUserSearch` | Debounced user search via `/api/users?q=` | `query, setQuery, results, isSearching, reset` |
| `useClickOutside` | Click-outside detection | Side effect (calls handler) |
| `useIsMobile` | Mobile breakpoint (< 768px) | `boolean` |

## Common Parameters
- `initialEntries` / `initialPosts` — SSR data to avoid client refetch
- `initialIsAdmin` — admin status from server
- `currentUserId` — for ownership checks
